{
  "stem": "3165.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And while we were in [POLISH], then I don't know-- for a short time-- then the Primacs found out that there was an orphanage for young children-- for survivors' children-- in Bielsko, in a different city, not far from [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my sister went there first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted me to stay on with them for awhile in this city, but my sister was in the orphanage first.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would visit her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so maybe I stayed with them-- probably in '45, maybe the end of '45.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were going on to Germany now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and, of course, I said, I'm going to go to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't say for us to come with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went, now, to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they went on to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we remained in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the conditions were very nice-- very nice personnel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a good question.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who ran it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Whether, you mean, it's the Polish government or--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Jewish-- It was a Jewish orphanage, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think New York-- Jewish Congress from New York helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember Jewish Congress of New  York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, I was eager to learn in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent us to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we had no schooling, so they put different-- didn't matter what ages, put in one room, one classroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And learned Polish-- studied Polish, everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then after a few months, they sort of put us in different grades, you know, according to age and how much fast you learn.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- I remember I was so anxious to learn and learned Polish real quick and studying Russian.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
